    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Transparency</h1>
      <p class="page-header__lede">
        A food publication that asks farms, restaurants, and food brands to show their work should show its own.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>Everything about how this site works is public. The code is open source under the MIT license. The recipes are licensed Creative Commons. Analytics are privacy-preserving and the dashboard link (if configured) is public. Corrections are logged on the original page. Editorial standards are written down on the ethics page. If we make a mistake, you will find it here before we try to hide it.</p>
    </div>

